                            <comment id="16313202" author="daniel_sun" created="Fri, 5 Jan 2018 14:33:00 +0000"  >&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Date().parse(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;yyy-MM-dd&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;2018-01-01&quot;&lt;/span&gt;) - 1).format(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;YYYY-MM-dd&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;The above code should be corrected as follows:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Date().parse(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;yyyy-MM-dd&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;2018-01-01&quot;&lt;/span&gt;) - 1).format(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;yyyy-MM-dd&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;P.S. The logic of parsing and formatting is same as the Java&apos;s&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
